Motorists are advised to avoid Hole-in-One Avenue in Ruimsig as well as surrounding areas such as Hendrik Potgieter Road, as protesters are currently turning violent at the Jim and Jerry s Driving Range, Roodepoort Record reports. It is rumoured that the protesters are allegedly baying for the blood of the owner of the driving range, accusing him of having shot a child in the nearby informal settlement. READ MORE: If you believe EFF is behind the protests &#8216;you&#8217;re a fool&#8217; Police and security company members are on the scene, where the protesters are keeping the employees of the driving range from leaving the premises. &#8211; Caxton News Service For more news your way, follow The Citizen on Facebook and Twitter.